control_panel.clipboard_text: Okuqukethwe kubhodi yokunameka yeseshini kuzotholakala endaweni yombhalo engezansi. Faka umbhalo endaweni yombhalo engezansi ukwenza okuqukethwe kutholakale kuseshini.

control_panel.share_text: Yabelana ngokuthola kuphela le seshini nabanye abasebenzisi.

control_panel.tips1: Noma yimuphi umsebenzisi onalesi sixhumanisi angabuka lesi seshini futhi ahlanganyele engxoxweni.
control_panel.tips2: Izinguquko ekuhlelweni kwevidiyo zithinta bonke ababukeli. Lapho ukwaba kunikwe amandla, isinqumo silungisiwe ngokuzenzakalelayo ukuqinisekisa okuhlangenwe nakho okungaguquki kwabo bonke ababukeli.
control_panel.the-control-panel-can-be-found: Iphaneli yokulawula ingatholakala ohlangothini lwesobunxele lwedeskithophu futhi ingasetshenziselwa ibhodi yokunamathisela, ukulanda, ukuphuma nokubhubhisa izici.

profile.ssh-private-key: Ukhiye we-SSH yangasese (Uhlobo: I-RSA, ifomethi: PEM)
profile.Session Usage Details: Last 30 Days: Imininingwane Yokusebenzisa Iseshini: Izinsuku ezingama-30 ezedlule
profile.auto_launch_text: Yethula ngokuzenzakalela iseshini ye-KASM lapho ungena ngemvume. Kusetshenziswa isithombe sokusebenza esizenzakalelayo.
profile.control_text: Vula bese uvala iphaneli yokulawula ngaphakathi kweseshini ye-KASM ngokuchofoza kabili ukhiye we-CTRL.
profile.default_text: Isithombe esizenzakalelayo sokusebenza ukuze uqalise lapho uchofoza i-Launch Manje Into yemenyu. Lesi sithombe siyasetshenziswa futhi uma isikhathi sokuvulwa kwe-auto sivunyelwe.
profile.key_pair_text: Vuselela i-SSH Key Pair efakwe ngokuzenzakalelayo esifundweni ngasinye seKasm uma ivunyelwe ngezinqubomgomo zokuphatha.
profile.logout: Manje uzobe ungenile. Ngena ngemvume ngeziqinisekiso ezintsha.
profile.private_key_text: Faka ukhiye wangasese ngezansi kanye ne-passphase yokhiye uma kudingeka. Ukhiye womphakathi uzokhishwa kukhiye wangasese. I-passphrase ayigcinwanga.
profile.sound_text: Nika amandla imiphumela yomsindo yengxoxo ngezikhathi ezabiwe.
profile.ssh_public_text: Ukhiye womphakathi we-SHS owayefakwe ngokuzenzakalelayo esifundweni ngasinye seKasm uma uvunyelwe izinqubomgomo zomlawuli.
profile.theme_text: Lungisa itimu yohlelo lokusebenza. I-Auto izosebenzisa izilungiselelo zezinhlelo zendawo ye-OS OS.
profile.tip_text: Khombisa amathiphu awusizo lapho wethula iseshini yeKasm.
profile.session-usage-details-last-30-: Imininingwane Yokusebenzisa Iseshini: Izinsuku ezingama-30 ezedlule
profile.ui-language-text: Setha ulimi olusetshenziswa kuyo yonke le nkundla yokuxhumana.

settings.auth-description: Izilungiselelo zomhlaba ezihlobene nokufakazelwa ubuqiniso kwiseva (kubandakanya), kufaka phakathi ukwengeza i-Google Recaptcha nezaziso esikrinini sokungena ngemvume. Hambisa ngaphezulu kwesihloko sokusetha ukubona amathuluzi.
settings.connections-description: Lezi zilungiselelo zisetshenziselwa ukuchaza uchungechunge lwamapharamitha okuxhumeka okuxhuma kwangaphandle kwe-RDP / SSH / KASMVNC Endpoints. Kuchazwa njengentambo eyodwa ye-json
settings.images-description: Izilungiselelo zomhlaba zokusetha ukuthi ukwengeza izikhala zokusebenza eqenjini ezenzakalelayo noma cha nokusetha indlela ezenzakalelayo ye-CPU Allocation.
settings.licensing-description: Ukusetha komhlaba wonke ukucacisa indawo kwiseva yelayisense
settings.logging-description: Izilungiselelo Zomhlaba wonke ukusetha izinketho zokugawula i-KASM. I-KASM inikezela ngokungena ngemvume okuphakathi ebhokisini, noma ngabe ufaka i-KASM yonke kwiseva eyodwa kuhlelo olusatshalaliswa ngamaseva e-API angaphendulwanga kanye nama-ejenti amaningi we-KASM, wonke ama-logs aqoqiwe futhi ahlanganiswe.
settings.manager-description: Izilungiselelo Zomhlaba wonke ukumisa umphathi, khumbula ukuqala kabusha izinsizakalo uma kudingeka.
settings.scale-description: Izilungiselelo Zomhlaba wonke zokulungiselela ukuthi izikali zikaKasm, kufaka phakathi ama-ejenti avumayo futhi amise ukuthi ukuhlanzwa kanjani kusingathwa kanjani.
settings.storage-description: Izilungiselelo Zomhlaba wonke zokulungiselela imininingwane yangaphandle yokugcina yento ukuze isetshenziswe nge-KASM yezinto ezinjengamaphrofayili aphikelelayo.
settings.theme-description: Izilungiselelo zomhlaba zokuhlelela ingqikithi zibukeka, njengokusetha isithombe sangemuva kwideshibhodi yomsebenzisi.
settings.web_filter-description: Izilungiselelo zomhlaba zokumisa isihlungi sewebhu, kufaka phakathi ukusetha indawo yesihlungi sewebhu ongayisebenzisa.

system_info.Are you sure you want to delete this lic: Uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukususa le layisense?
system_info.export_configuration_description: Le nketho ikuvumela ukuthi uthumele ukucushwa konke kohlelo lwakho, ngaphandle kwezingodo. Ukucushwa kuzolandwa kufayela elibethelwe le-AES256 elibethelwe le-AES256 Ebhaliwe. Ungadinga ukusetshenziswa okufana ne-7Zip ukukhombisa.
system_info.export_schema_description: Le nketho ikuvumela ukuthi uthumele i-Schema yokucushwa kwesistimu (Isakhiwo sedatha). Lokhu kungasiza lapho kwakha ukucushwa kwangokwezifiso ze-yaml futhi kungukuthi analojius kwi-database schema dump.
system_info.import_config_description: Le nketho ikuvumela ukuthi ungenise ukucushwa kohlelo lwakho lonke. Ukungenisa akungezi ku-Cruig ekhona ekhona - kuyayithatha esikhundleni. Le nqubo iyi-analogous ekusebenzeni kwedatha yokubuyisela.
system_info.details-description: Imininingwane mayelana nesistimu efaka inguqulo ye-Web UI esebenzayo kanye ne-ID yokufaka
system_info.db-details-description: Imininingwane eyisisekelo mayelana nesizindalwazi samanje, okuhlanganisa umsingathi nenguqulo.
system_info.api-details-description: Ulwazi mayelana ne-API yamanje, okuhlanganisa inguqulo nomsingathi.
system_info.license-details-description: Imininingwane mayelana nanoma iyiphi ilayisensi esetshenziswa njengamanje.

tooltip.add_images_to_default_group: Ngeza ngokuzenzakalela izindawo zokusebenzela eqenjini ezenzakalelayo lapho kungezwa khona izindawo zokusebenzela ezintsha.
tooltip.agent_version: Lokhu kulungiselelwa kusetshenziselwa ukukhawulela ukuthi yimaphi ama-ejenti we-KASM avunyelwe ukuxhumana nomphathi.
tooltip.anonymous_user_expiration: Uma kulungiselelwe, ama-akhawunti angaziwa womsebenzisi azosuswa ngokuzenzakalelayo ngemuva kwalesi sikhathi sesikhathi esichaziwe emahoreni.
tooltip.api_private_key: Ukhiye wangasese usetshenziselwa ukusayina isicelo phakathi kwezakhi ze-KASM.
tooltip.api_public_cert: Ukhiye womphakathi osetshenziswa yizinto ze-KASM zokuqinisekisa izingcingo zangaphakathi ze-API.
tooltip.debug_retention: Inani lamahora wokugcina izingodo ze-KASM Debug zasendaweni. Isexwayiso - bona amadokhumenti we-kasm ngaphambi kokulungiswa.
tooltip.default_cpu_allocation_method: Imisa isu elizenzakalelayo le-CPU Lokwabiwa kwezithombe zesitsha. Izinketho ezivumelekile yizilinganiso noma amasheya.
tooltip.default_vm_rdp_connection_settings: Izilungiselelo zokuxhuma okuzenzakalelayo ze-VM RDP izikhathi.
tooltip.default_vm_ssh_connection_settings: Izilungiselelo zokuxhumeka okuzenzakalelayo ze-VM SSH SESS.
tooltip.default_vm_vnc_connection_settings: Izilungiselelo zokuxhumeka okuzenzakalelayo ze-VN VNC izikhathi.
tooltip.enable_kasm_auth: Dinga izicelo zeklayenti ku-kasm yokuqukethwe njengokulandwayo nokulayishwa okumele kugunyazwe ukuthi kugunyazwe i-Token yeseshini yamanje yomsebenzisi.
tooltip.forward_inter_zone_agent_requests: Lapho uthintana ama-ejenti endaweni ehlukile, izicelo eziphambili ngekheli elihlukile le-Proxy's Proxy.
tooltip.guardian_interval: Inani lemizuzwana phakathi kokuhlolwa kwemenenja ye-API ye-Agent, kanye nokutholakala kweKasm.
tooltip.guardian_provision_threads: Inani lemicu ye-Manager API Server esebenzisa imisebenzi yokuqothula kanye nokuhlinzekelwa kwemisebenzi.
tooltip.hec_token: Ithokheni ye-Spulfunk Hec esetshenziselwa ukuqinisekiswa kwamalogi kwiseva ye-spunk.
tooltip.host_dead_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana selokhu kwahlolwa okokugcina kwe-ejenti ngaphambi kokukumaka njengokufile. Amaseva ashonile abhujiswa ngokuzenzakalela uma ngabe anikezwe amandla.
tooltip.host_missing_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana selokhu kwahlolwa okokugcina kwe-ejenti ngaphambi kokukumaka njengokufile.
tooltip.http_method: Indlela ye-HTTP yokusebenzisa, amanani avumelekile athunyelwe futhi abeke. I-Spbhamunk isebenzisa okuthunyelwe ngenkathi i-Elastics Search API isebenzisa ukubeka
tooltip.https_insecure: Setha iqiniso uma iseva yokugawula okukude ingenayo i-CERT esayiniwe yeSitifiketi Somphakathi.
tooltip.kasm_auth_domain: Faka ngaphezulu kwesizinda esisetshenziswe kwikhukhi yeseshini yeKasm.
tooltip.keepalive_expiration: Amaklayenti ahlala athumela izicelo ze-Gcinaive uma ungene ku-kasm. Leli nani liyinombolo yemizuzwana i-KASM izohlala isebenza ngemuva kokutholwa kokugcina.
tooltip.launcher_background_url: I-URL esetshenziselwa ukucacisa isithombe sangemuva sesiqalisi.
tooltip.log_host: Igama leqembu noma ikheli le-IP leseva yokugawula okukude, ayisebenzi ngokugawulwa kwangaphakathi.
tooltip.log_port: Itheku okufanele lilisebenzise ngokungena ngemvume ngokungena ngemvume.
tooltip.log_protocol: Iphrothokholi yokugawula esetshenzisiwe, amanani avunyelwe angaphakathi, https, splunk, kanye ne-Elastics
tooltip.log_retention: Inani lezinsuku zokugcina izingodo ze-kasm zasendaweni. Isexwayiso - bona amadokhumenti we-kasm ngaphambi kokulungiswa.
tooltip.login_assistance: Inika amandla isixhumanisi sosizo lokungena ngemvume ekhasini lokungena ngemvume ku-URL efakiwe. Akuboniswanga uma inani alinalutho.
tooltip.manager_expiration: Inani lemizuzwana kuze kube yilapho umphathi ibhekwa engatholakali unomphela, ngasiphi isikhathi umbiko wemenenja ezosuswa database. Inani le-0 likhubaza isheke lokuphelelwa yisikhathi.
tooltip.max_login_attempts: Inani lemizamo yokungena elingalungile ngaphambi kokuthi i-akhawunti ikhiyiwe. Lokhu kusebenza kusebenza kuphela kuma-akhawunti endawo.
tooltip.minimize_local_logging: Lapho usebenzisa isixazululo sokugawula okukude njenge-splunk, unciphise ukugawulwa kwemininingwane yendawo ukuze uthole ukukala okungcono.
tooltip.primary_manager_timeout: Inani lemizuzwana kuze kube yilapho umphathi eyinhloko ebhekwa njengengatholakali. Uma abanye abaphathi bephila umuntu uzothatha indima eyinhloko.
tooltip.provision_timeout: Inani eliphakeme lesikhathi sokulinda i-VMS ekhuliswe ngokuzenzakalela ukuze ungene ngaphakathi futhi itholakale. Ngemuva kwalesi sikhathi seqiwe, i-VM ichithwa ngokuzenzakalela.
tooltip.registration_token: Ithokheni esetshenziselwa ukuzibhalisa izingxenye ezintsha ekuthumelweni.
tooltip.same_site: Ilungiselela isici se-Sames. Izinketho ezivumelekile ziyi-LAX, ngokuqinile futhi akekho.
tooltip.same_zone_reply: Uma kusethwe kuliqiniso, umphathi uzophendula kuphela ekuthumbeni kwenhliziyo ye-ejenti ngohlu lwabaphathi endaweni efanayo. Ngaphandle kwalokho uhlu lwabo bonke abaphathi lunikezwe. Lokhu kuvumela ama-ejenti ukuthi ahluleke kubaphathi kwezinye izindawo.
tooltip.token: Ithokheni yokufakazela ubuqiniso esetshenziswe ekuxhumaneni phakathi kwama-KASM Agents kanye nemenenja ye-API Server.
tooltip.token_drift_max: Mangaki amaminithi we-totp kufanele avunyelwe ukudonsa.
tooltip.update_check: Lokhu kulungiselelwa kuzovimba umphathi ukuthi abheke izibuyekezo zohlelo lwe-KASM.
tooltip.url_endpoint: I-Splunk Endpoint, okungenzeka kakhulu / insiza / umqoqi / umcimbi. Kwe-Elastics Search kuzobe kuyinkomba / _doc /.
tooltip.web_filter_update_url: I-URL esetshenziselwa ukuvuselela i-database yokuhlukanisa izihlungi zewebhu
tooltip.cleanup_orphaned_autoscale_servers: Uma isistimu iphazamiseka noma amaphutha phakathi ne-AutoScaling iseva inganikezwa ngokwengxenye futhi isistimu ingase ilahlekelwe umkhondo wokuthi iseva iyenza intandane. Lokhu kusebenzisa izinsiza uhlelo olungakwazi ukuhlinzeka ngazo. Ukunika amandla lesi silungiselelo kuvumela isistimu ukuthi isebenzise i-heuristics ukuthola nokucekela phansi izinsiza eziyizintandane.
